You know, I thought I had given some sort of description of Sector H in this article, but upon re-reading it I realized I hadn't. There's really nothing particularly special about it. It's mainly supposed to be a storage area for safe SCPs and anomalous items that have been deemed unimportant or unable to be researched further. I'll have to add that info somewhere. I'll consider adding more info on Brandt as well, even if it's just a footnote.







